<h3 id="-or-reporting-bugs">… or reporting bugs</h3>
<p>If you lack the time or knowledge to do any of the above, just using Gitea and sharing the word is enough to make us happy! One thing you can always do is to report any bugs you find on the <a href="https://github.com/go-gitea/gitea/issues">Gitea issue tracker</a>.</p>
<p>Before opening an issue, read the <a href="https://github.com/go-gitea/gitea/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#bug-reports">contribution guidelines about reporting bugs</a>. After opening an issue, try to stick around a while to answer any questions we might have. Replies greatly help us find the root cause of an issue.</p>
